Please refer to the 1st page of this book:source: http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr;=&id;=NcmXvBX--agC&oi;=fnd&pg;=PR3&dq;=adoption+law&ots;=bMKbElPtsd&sig;=EGnN46PrECgKj75qw1uluX0GcnM#PPA1,M1 You will find that adoption is considered: the creation of a parent-child relationship by judicial order between two parties who usually are unrelated.
